These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: kale, pumpkin
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the person eating pumpkin##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pumpkin   | kale  |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: spinach, grapefruit
2 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the snake is not the person eating grapefruit##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | spinach | grapefruit      |
| Pet    | snake  | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
