.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, comedy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, badminton
1. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
2. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | comedy |
| Sport         | badminton | rugby      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, pop
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, russian
1. the fan country is on the far right##1
2. the fan pop is not the mexican##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | country      |
| Nationality   | russian | mexican |

