.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, writer
2 different pets are kept: bird, snake
1. the bartender is in an odd position##4
2. the bartender is not the owner of the snake##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | bartender | writer |
| Pet   | bird       | snake       |

